doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    title
  body
    table(style='width: 700px; padding: 15px;')
      tr
        td(style='text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #ff5e00;')
          img(src=model.serverUrl + "/logo")
      tr
        td(style='text-align: center; border-top: 2px solid #ff5e00;')
      tr
        td
          h2(style='font-size: 20px; font-family: Arial; color: #323232;') Hey #{model.user.profile.firstName},
      | .
      tr
        td
          p(style='font-size: 20px; font-family: Arial; color: #00bfff; margin: 0px;') Thank you for your Order
      tr
        td
          p(style='font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #323232; margin: 0px; line-height: 28px; padding-top: 10px;')
            | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
      tr
        td
          table(style='width: 100%; padding-top: 50px;', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
            tr
